    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781160/extras/cb76c1f5411df4260e5ec38af310d064.poster.avif?t=1728899608\" width=600 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781160/extras/cb76c1f5411df4260e5ec38af310d064.webm?t=1728899608\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781160/extras/cb76c1f5411df4260e5ec38af310d064.mp4?t=1728899608\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>从你还是个孩子的时候，你就想成为像你老爸一样的电工。现在机会来了，他决定教你一些电工工作的基本常识，以便你在自己入行后能更容易地开始工作。如果你能和爸爸一起待在家里，学习一些有用的东西，为什么要在学校假期期间出去度假呢?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>记住。这只是你作为一名电工的冒险的开始!</strong></h2><u>这是电工模拟器游戏的一个免费的游戏序章。 </u><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>主要特点</strong>[/u]</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781160/extras/9167694e809768e22a801c321760b96c.webp?t=1728899608\" width=20 height=20 /></span><strong>修理</strong> 插座和开关。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781160/extras/9167694e809768e22a801c321760b96c.webp?t=1728899608\" width=20 height=20 /></span><strong>铺设</strong>电线<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781160/extras/9167694e809768e22a801c321760b96c.webp?t=1728899608\" width=20 height=20 /></span><strong>弄好</strong>工作台上的设备<br><br><strong>进行修理</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781160/extras/793407f8db5530c4ad3289b2181aacf2.poster.avif?t=1728899608\" width=600 height=276 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781160/extras/793407f8db5530c4ad3289b2181aacf2.webm?t=1728899608\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781160/extras/793407f8db5530c4ad3289b2181aacf2.mp4?t=1728899608\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>制造商的保修期只有很短的时间，而且新的电器很贵。修理一些小的电器设备赚些快钱。<br><br><strong>日光灯/灯泡</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781160/extras/44e8db25a91ee9c53d1ddf305b271ad0.poster.avif?t=1728899608\" width=600 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781160/extras/44e8db25a91ee9c53d1ddf305b271ad0.webm?t=1728899608\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781160/extras/44e8db25a91ee9c53d1ddf305b271ad0.mp4?t=1728899608\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>为不同的室内环境带来能量和光线。<br><br><strong>最终成果</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781160/extras/d12f18be94c03cd737b698e6683f20ad.poster.avif?t=1728899608\" width=600 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781160/extras/d12f18be94c03cd737b698e6683f20ad.webm?t=1728899608\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781160/extras/d12f18be94c03cd737b698e6683f20ad.mp4?t=1728899608\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <br>你和你的客户们都想看到一个令人惊叹的最终成果。把那些暗淡的室内环境点亮，给那些老旧的插头接上电，或者完全断电。",
